title: 2nd International Conference for Startups
desc: The event will take place at Google Campus over two floors, so expect to meet a lot of migrant entrepreneurs, business owners from all over the world that wil be travelling to attend this exciting event! Join us if you would like to receive advice on tax, marketing, branding, networking, mentoring, sales, growing your team, which technology you should use in your business and also you will be able to attend talks, workshops and learn how to import or export, as well as learn how to do business with countries like Mexico, Argentina and Turkey to name a few. It will be a great opportunity to meet fellow migrant entrepreneurs and grow your list of contacts. We look forward to meeting you there! The International conference for Startup team.
